data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. **SANTA STOP HERE!!!!  SELLER IS READY TO CONSIDER YOUR OFFER ** - **CLEAN 4 POINT INSPECTION ** This is a MUST SEE!! *** Step into your own Florida paradise with this delightful 2-bedroom, 1 1/2 bathroom home, ready for immediate move-in! Nestled within the enchanting Greenbriar community in the heart of Clearwater, Florida, this EXCEPTIONALLY CLEAN & WELL-MAINTAINED home is a homeowner's dream. Upon arrival, you'll be instantly charmed by simple landscaping and curb appeal. With this, the Owner is providing a property, that is absolutely ready to create the yard scape that you have always wanted to design & impress.  Once inside, a roomy open floor plan bathed in natural light awaits with classic mid-century terrazzo flooring throughout. The living room seamlessly connects to the formal dining area, which is conveniently adjacent to the kitchen and a delightful, enclosed patio. This home provides all the essentials for a comfortable lifestyle.  But there's even more to this gem! The kitchen boasts a few new stainless-steel appliances, a new sink, and a timeless tile backsplash. The interior and exterior of the home have received fresh coats of paint, the roof was replaced in 2016, and it is prepped to pass a 4-point inspection with ease. The main bathroom offers ample space and features a bathtub complemented by a sizable vanity. Both bedrooms are roomy and offer plenty of closet space and you will love the one-car attached garage with fresh epoxy coated flooring!  For extra living space, the enclosed Florida room beckons, offering a tranquil spot to unwind and savor the peaceful backyard views. The spacious backyard is a blank canvas, inviting the addition of a pool or the creation of your very own tropical oasis. Location-wise, this home is hard to beat, with easy access to both the Gulf and the Bay, ensuring you're just moments away from the best Florida beaches and waterways.  Embrace the sense of community with access to the neighborhood pool and a calendar full of social events, including holiday parties, poolside gatherings, and card and shuffleboard tournaments. What truly distinguishes this residence is its exceptional location, a mere 5-minute drive to Downtown Dunedin, renowned for its dining and vibrant nightlife. Plus, you are located less than 15 minutes to St. Pete/Clearwater Airport and 20-25 minutes to Tampa International Airport. Nearby, you'll find an array of shopping centers, grocery stores, gas stations, and pharmacies, streamlining your daily errands.  Don’t miss this rare opportunity to live in Greenbriar, one of Clearwater's most coveted neighborhoods! So why delay? Make this spectacular home yours – schedule a private viewing today! (Main Roof in 2016, Secondary Roof in 2016, Water Heater in 2015, Electrical Panel updated & HVAC in 2016.)**Recent 4 point inspection is CLEAR AND CLEAN!**
